OpenDMR Decoder - AMBE+2 Vocoder Decoder
=========================================

This decoder is derived from mbelib-neo by arancormonk, which is itself
based on the original mbelib by Pavel Yazev.

Original mbelib:
  Copyright (C) 2010 Pavel Yazev
  https://github.com/szechyjs/mbelib

mbelib-neo enhancements:
  Copyright (C) 2023 arancormonk
  - Improved audio synthesis using PFFFT
  - Adaptive spectral enhancement
  - Code cleanup and modernization

PFFFT (Pretty Fast FFT):
  Copyright (C) 2013 Julien Pommier
  https://bitbucket.org/jpommier/pffft
  Based on FFTPACK by Paul Swarztrauber

This code is licensed under the GNU General Public License v2.0 (GPL-2.0).
